{
    "text": "What about Ghost?",
    "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:16:25 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "<b>Bob Sassone writes via email</b>:",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:16:33 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "You said on your blog that you can't imagine moving from WordPress because \"there isn't anything else out there that's offering something new for the writers.\" What about Ghost? ",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:18:45 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "Bob's site is <a href=\"https://www.bobsassone.com/\">bobsassone.com</a>.",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:21:24 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "<b>My response</b>:",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:18:16 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "Sorry it wasn't clear -- but as far as I know, Ghost isn't built on WordPress. It's a completely different product. ",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:19:50 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "My writing app runs on WordPress. So you can use it with your existing wordpress.com sites.",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:20:14 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "It's a browser-based JavaScript app that hooks into WordPress via the wpidentity package I wrote.",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:31:02 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "And the codebase I've built will support lots of editors built using WordPress as the backend. ",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:20:42 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "A <a href=\"https://github.com/scripting/Scripting-News/issues/312\">place</a> to ask questions. ",
            "created": "Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:28:48 GMT",
            "isComment": "true",
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}